dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents Bike Lanes for New Orleans, LA in 2018. Completed bike lanes across the public street network of New Orleans. Updated regularly by DPW to reflect recently completed lanes. Attributed to show the type, for example a lane shared with cars or one protected from traffic. This file was downloaded on December, 2018 by NYU Data Services. It was originally represented on the New Orleans Open Data Socrata portal as catalog record 8npz-j6vy
dc_title_s: Bike Lanes for New Orleans, LA, 2018
